snippet.title: Triple Take Trailer [Official]
snippet.description:
Triple Take is a fast 2D precision platformer where the stage evolves as you complete it! Run, wall jump, climb and swim through increasingly difficult levels in vibrant colored worlds!

RELEASE DATE 6th of October. 

Triple Take on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1734250/Triple_Take
